						<h3 class="feature-title">Professional Reports</h3>
						<p class="feature-description">Upgrade to detailed $39 professional reports with comprehensive analysis, market comparisons, and actionable insights.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-item">
						<div class="feature-icon">üèÜ</div>
						<h3 class="feature-title">Proven Methodology</h3>
						<p class="feature-description">Based on industry-standard SDE analysis used by business brokers, lenders, and professional appraisers.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
